	<abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">
		Physician and chairman of the Counselor Committee for the Smith College Health Service and Infirmary. Contains correspondence, pamphlets, publications, clippings, budget reports, and photograph album. 
	</abstract>
